+  // CopyWith method to create a new instance with modified values
+  NotificationModel copyWith({
+    DateTime? date,
+    bool? sms,
+    bool? email,
+    bool? push,
+  }) {

+      date: date ?? this.date,
+      sms: sms ?? this.sms,
+      email: email ?? this.email,
+      push: push ?? this.push,
+    );
